snippet: Corey Dickerson hit Atlanta catcher Gerald Laird with his backswing and tempers quickly flared, setting off a tense sequence and leading to several ejections Thursday as the Colorado Rockies beat the Braves 10-3....

headline.print_headline: Tempers Flare as Rockies Beat Braves 10-3
headline.main: Tempers Flare as Rockies Beat Braves 10-3

lead_paragraph: Corey Dickerson hit Atlanta catcher Gerald Laird with his backswing and tempers quickly flared, setting off a tense sequence and leading to several ejections Thursday as the Colorado Rockies beat the Braves 10-3.
